            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> &amp;lt;M=VI&amp;gt;(aximo) <lb n="2"/>et Iunoni <expan><abbr>Reg</abbr><ex>inae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Genio loci <lb n="4"/>et <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>eabusque</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>omnib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Sedulius <lb n="6"/>Iulianus m<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>il</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="7"/>le&amp;lt;g=S&amp;gt;(ionis) VIII <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> A<supplied reason="lost">n</supplied><lb break="no" n="8"/>toninian<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>pro <expan><abbr>sal</abbr><ex>ute</ex></expan> sua et <expan><abbr>suor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">s</supplied>tat</abbr><ex>ione</ex></expan> iterat&amp;lt;a=O&amp;gt; posuit <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omino</ex></expan></supplied> &amp;lt;n=IVI&amp;gt;(ostro) Antonin&amp;lt;o=I&amp;gt; <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> PETVR </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost">et <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan></supplied> 
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die vorspringende corona ist ringsum, die crepido vorne abgeschlagen. Der Stein wurde bereits in der frühen Neuzeit sekundär überarbeitet. In Z. 10 stand ursprünglich möglicherweise nur posuit; vom Stifter könnte bei der erneuten Stationierung am Fundort der Inschrift die Konsulatsangabe hinzugefügt worden sein, die später aber offenbar entstellt wurde. Z. 12 muß sich auf der crepido befunden haben. - (B): Z. 1: Filtzinger; CIL, Schallmayer: Iovi. 3: CIL: [et] Genio. Z. 8: Schallmayer: Antoninian&amp;lt;a&amp;gt;e. Z. 10: iterat(a); Cubaynes: Z. 1: Iovi; Z. 3: [et]; Z. 11: p(osuit) et v(otum) r(etulit). Autopsie R. Wiegels.</p>
            </div>
